{"tid":82530,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"希古恩：會建議美斯來祖記跟我合作","createTime":"2017-01-16T04:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T10:17:09.000Z","uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54c70e21910d183e61b1d4f0c60a0495cc6eb25d","tid":82530,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T04:34:38.000Z","msg":"上週末，祖雲達斯前鋒希古恩接受採訪，他表示自己會邀請美斯來祖記效力。<br />\n<br />\n　　在接受採訪時，希古恩說：「<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我當然會建議美斯來祖雲達斯踢球，意甲是個很難踢的聯賽</span></span>，尤其是這裡的防守很強。我不知道美斯或者C.朗拿度能否在意甲還進那麼多球，事實就是意甲很難踢。意甲讓我有所收穫，我在這裡取得了進步。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「祖雲達斯和皇馬很相似，幾乎就是這裡的皇馬，不論是在祖記還是皇馬，目標都是闖進每項賽事的決賽，兩支球隊的要求都非常高。雖然踢法上有所不同，但心裡想的都是贏得一切。」希古恩表示。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63e054c5e713aa03704f8303e907ce257c16c92","tid":82530,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T04:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7817bb3fe792b3753745c797e52dfddeaec2d88f","tid":82530,"uid":66593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T04:36:44.000Z","msg":"梅西：屌你呀"},{"pid":"5319904f6cab98928685da5de49fbebd664cb5d6","tid":82530,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T04:41:22.000Z","msg":"表面： 不了 留巴做名宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n內心講<br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你條pk<br />\n次次見親你都無好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c3e80ea5701c8d07bb4c3a4bef1b84edb7c755","tid":82530,"uid":55256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T04:46:24.000Z","msg":"祖雲達斯和皇馬很相似，幾乎就是這裡的皇馬，不論是在祖記還是皇馬，目標都是闖進每